# The Android Open Source Project build system does not use Gradle by default anymore in
# recent versions of Android Studio, but still uses it in older versions and to build independent
# gradle wrapper projects.
# The actual properties of the displays are unknown.
# Because we want to keep the wrapper properties in the repository (to be able to build the project)
# we should keep it.
!gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
!gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.properties
